889
00:39:55,699 --> 00:39:56,780
No rush, it's fine.

890
00:39:56,780 --> 00:39:57,860
I'm in a hurry to get home.

891
00:39:58,699 --> 00:39:59,360
Okay.

892
00:39:59,800 --> 00:40:01,179
We're off.

893
00:40:01,179 --> 00:40:02,139
Bye, Jing.

894
00:40:04,000 --> 00:40:04,860
- Let's go.
- Wait a second.

895
00:40:06,579 --> 00:40:07,659
I swear that guy back there

896
00:40:07,659 --> 00:40:08,659
looked exactly like...

897
00:40:09,079 --> 00:40:09,639
It's true.

898
00:40:14,340 --> 00:40:15,159
Not drinking it?

899
00:40:15,659 --> 00:40:17,079
I'm not helping you if you bleed again.

900
00:40:21,019 --> 00:40:22,179
You ran off the second you saw them.

901
00:40:22,239 --> 00:40:23,119
Scared of being seen together?

902
00:40:28,500 --> 00:40:29,739
I just didn't wanna put you on the spot.

903
00:40:33,260 --> 00:40:34,960
Sounds like you're looking out for me.

904
00:40:35,260 --> 00:40:36,860
If it's true, you shouldn't have

905
00:40:36,860 --> 00:40:38,079
joined Haoyun at all.

906
00:40:41,940 --> 00:40:42,920
Are you hiding some tricky scheme

907
00:40:42,920 --> 00:40:43,940
up your sleeve?

908
00:40:47,099 --> 00:40:47,739
Not at all.

909
00:40:50,679 --> 00:40:51,320
Chen Yi,

910
00:40:51,980 --> 00:40:52,820
promise me

911
00:40:53,460 --> 00:40:54,840
you won't pull those petty stunts

912
00:40:55,500 --> 00:40:57,320
that push me away like you used to.

913
00:40:58,159 --> 00:40:59,159
Don't leave me behind again,

914
00:40:59,980 --> 00:41:00,599
okay?

915
00:41:05,460 --> 00:41:06,280
Then you promise me too,

916
00:41:08,000 --> 00:41:09,000
no more dangerous stuff.

917
00:41:16,159 --> 00:41:16,860
You hear me?

918
00:41:39,900 --> 00:41:40,460
Here, eat.

919
00:41:40,460 --> 00:41:41,280
Before it gets cold.

920
00:41:55,320 --> 00:41:55,880
What's wrong?

921
00:41:56,320 --> 00:41:57,079
Is there something on my face?

922
00:41:57,599 --> 00:41:58,039
No.

923
00:42:01,500 --> 00:42:02,219
Then what are you looking at?

924
00:42:03,320 --> 00:42:04,340
Just looking.

925
00:42:14,099 --> 00:42:16,079
You really do look great in a suit.

926
00:42:16,840 --> 00:42:18,079
Can't take my eyes off you.

927
00:42:20,940 --> 00:42:21,760
We're at the office building now.

928
00:42:22,280 --> 00:42:22,940
So?

929
00:42:23,400 --> 00:42:24,260
You said it yourself.

930
00:42:24,260 --> 00:42:25,920
You wore a suit to my workplace

931
00:42:25,920 --> 00:42:26,480
so I'd only have eyes

932
00:42:26,480 --> 00:42:27,400
for you.

933
00:42:27,719 --> 00:42:28,139
So here I am,

934
00:42:28,139 --> 00:42:29,159
staring at you properly.
